@SleeperHQ @DFBeanCounter About sources for the data, most of this data comes from the #nflverse https://t.co/ijrz5J3FXE. My most sincere thanks to all the guys involved in that project for the amount of work they put into it. Some other metric come direct or indirectly from Next Gen Stats.
19/24

Major thanks to @_TanHo for all his guidance and expertise. The new ecosystem is largely borrowed from the awesome #nflverse, so his help has been invaluable. Also: huge thanks to @agale137 and @Austin_LC_RL for beta testing this and giving me great feedback.

ESPN's catch score has a strong correlation with the #nflverse's completion percentage over expectation (CPOE). 

Wide receivers that scored well in this metric have a positive influence on the QB's expected completion percentage. https://t.co/tfbzYeAh70
